API Spec
========

*we need to authenticate the user before doing these

Login (POST)
	index.php/api/auth/login
	index.php/api/auth/create
	index.php/api/auth/test

Question (GET/POST)
	index.php/api/question/post
	index.php/api/question/details
	index.php/api/question/delete
	index.php/api/question/update

Answer
	index.php/api/answer/post/
	index.php/api/answer/details
	index.php/api/answer/delete
	index.php/api/answer/update

Vote
	index.php/api/vote/voteup/question/id
	index.php/api/vote/votedown/question/id

Tags
	index.php/api/tag/post/question/id
	index.php/api/tag/delete/question/id
	index.php/api/tag/update/question/id
	index.php/api/tag/get/question/id

	index.php/api/tags/all

Search
	index.php/api/search/questions/Q+
	index.php/api/search/questions/advanced/Q+

	index.php/api/search/users/Q+

	index.php/api/search/tags/Q+


